snippet.title: Doom & Destiny Worlds - Survive without Wi-Fi Trailer
snippet.description:
When Destiny calls for help, but no one answers, four ordinary nerds are randomly chosen instead. Armed with hand crafted weapons and bad jokes, can four nerds survive and defeat three almighty tyrants and find their way home?

Available on Nintendo eShop: https://doomanddestiny.net/scripts/redirect_ddw_ns.php

Available on STEAM: https://bit.ly/3l79Orr
